nodes.text: X-Wing: Books 1-3 is the unabridged audio version of the Legends novels X-Wing: Rogue Squadron, X-Wing: Wedge's Gamble, and X-Wing: The Krytos Trap by author Michael A. Stackpole. The audiobook was performed by Alec Volz and was released by the American Printing House for the Blind in 2019.
